										<p>Dude, what an unbelievably horrific &amp; sordid state of affairs. I had no idea that the (required) antivirus software on PC&#39;s was just as intrusive &amp; destructive as the (unnecessary) antivirus software on Macs!</p>
<p>I am so sorry that you have to put up with all of that SHIT. You are absolutely right &#8212; all of that crap is MALWARE. Including IE7, which you can never remove from your PC.</p>
